pageContext.claim: “We put the strongest sanctions you can imagine but they get a lot, we have a lot in store if they don't have an impact, including massive tariffs on steel.”
pageContext.analysis: This is false. Trump has the power to impose more sanctions and has yet to target some of Turkey’s most valuable resources. The Washington Post reported the sanctions are “mostly bluster,” according to economist Jacob Funk Kirkegaard of the Peterson Institute for International Economics.
